rows.label: tev035991_MSG0001
rows.name:
This is the worst day of my life, isn't it?
What am I going to doooooo?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035991_MSG0002
rows.name: Oh, wait! You! Can you help, maybe?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035991_MSG0003
rows.name:
...Wow, I can't believe that that actually worked.
I guess screaming loudly and looking upset actually
pays off, doesn't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035991_MSG0004
rows.name:
It turns out that I dropped my comm device somewhere,
and I CANNOT live without it, you understand?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035991_MSG0005
rows.name:
It's pretty much the only way I have of contacting my
friends when I want to hang out, isn't it? And how
else can I surf FrontierNav when I'm bored?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035991_MSG0006
rows.name:
Anyway, I'm sure you can see how this is a really
horrible situation, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035991_MSG0007
rows.name:
And look, I'm not going to ask you to find it for me,
but do you think you could at least maybe point me in
the the direction of a good intel dealer?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035991_JNK0010
rows.name: Suggest[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035991_SEL0011
rows.name: Tell Veverta to speak with Cheche the intel dealer.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035991_JNK0020
rows.name: Extort[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035991_SEL0021
rows.name:
Demand an introduction fee for
introducing Veverta to an info dealer.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035991_MSG0008
rows.name:
That's a Nopon, yes? Good idea. I bet this Cheche
character could find my device in no time, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035991_MSG0009
rows.name: I'll get in touch with him and see, I suppose?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035991_MSG0010
rows.name:
...What's that? Cheche's services cost money?
Er, how how much money?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035991_MSG0011
rows.name:
...Wait, THAT MUCH? Nope. Nope nope nope.
Forget it, all right? To pay those kind of fees,
I'd need to to get a job.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035991_MSG0012
rows.name:
I'd rather be bored than complicate my life with
something as taxing as actual labor, if you follow?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035991_MSG0013
rows.name:
And here I thought you came along to help, maybe?
Nice try, con artist![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035991_MSG0014
rows.name:
If it's going to cost me money, then forget it, all right?
I'll just learn to to live without a device...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035991_MSG0015
rows.name: But I'll be free, you know? So so free.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035991_MSG0016
rows.name:
Wow, I feel great now! Like I just took the shackles
of life and and unshackled them, you know?
Thanks, unscrupulous person![ST:wait ]
